	lib-imap-client: When server sends BYE before disconnection, log it
	as the reason.
	[55624c42bfb8]

	* src/lib-storage/index/imapc/imapc-list.c:
	imapc: When deleting a mailbox, unselect the current one just in
	case they're the same.
	[cc243b748a1c]

