	Reverted the previous change and fixed it the right way.
	[cf898dbcbffb]

	* src/doveadm/dsync/doveadm-dsync.c, src/lib-storage/mail-user.h,
	src/plugins/acl/acl-api.c, src/plugins/acl/acl-attributes.c,
