	imap-quota: GETQUOTAROOT command used UTF-8 instead of mUTF-7
	encoding for mailbox name.
	[90270c054e1f]

	* src/plugins/imap-acl/imap-acl-plugin.c:
	imap-acl: MYRIGHTS command used UTF-8 instead of mUTF-7 encoding for
	mailbox name.
	[880af3c78df9]

