	lib-index: Added mail_cache_view_update_cache_decisions()
	[4a19aea565f7]

	* NEWS, TODO, configure.in, src/doveadm/doveadm-mail-list-iter.c,
	src/doveadm/server-connection.c, src/lib-index/mail-index.c, src
