	backends. Moved struct index_search_context to index-search-
	private.h and added recheck_index_args flag that backends can set.
	[b96efbad2fa4]

	* src/util/script.c:
	script: Root permissions weren't being dropped before executing the
	script.
	[40f668d36547]

