	[77075d202fc1]

	* src/auth/auth-settings.c:
	auth: Fail if auth_cache_size value is too small.
	[27d235096cca]

	* src/auth/auth-cache.c:
	auth: Don't crash if auth_cache_size has a very small value.
	[9dc3c6de6e82]

	* src/login-common/client-common-auth.c:
