	[28639e01a479] <HEAD>

	* src/dsync/dsync-brain.c:
	dsync: Another try at not increasing mailbox uidnext/highestmodseq
	on failure
	[49b226835cd2] <HEAD>

	* src/lib-storage/list/mailbox-list-delete.c, src/lib-storage/list
