	instead of /tmp.
	[ae84eb604f84] <HEAD>

	* src/plugins/listescape/listescape-plugin.c:
	listescape: Fixed listing INBOX when namespace prefix was used.
	[4ba05c3702be] <HEAD>

2010-05-17  Timo Sirainen  <tss@iki.fi>

