	error.
	[20963e8ec560] <HEAD>

	* src/master/service.c:
	master: inet_listener {port=0} and unix/fifo_listener {mode=0} now
	disables it.
	[476de3a45cf8] <HEAD>

	* configure.in:
	configure: Fixed Berkeley DB check to not give an error.
	[db89ece5a19d] <HEAD>

