	to _DONT_LOG_TO_STDERR.
	[0dbc2dc0877c] <HEAD>

	* src/imap/imap-fetch.c:
	imap code cleanup: Use array instead of buffer for storing fetch
	handlers.
	[d6eda52bd74b] <HEAD>

	* src/imap/imap-fetch.c, src/imap/imap-fetch.h, src/imap/main.c:
